  In fact, Jeremiah quotes quite a long verbatim text from Micah (38
  characters). Other than that, the non-verbatim quoted text is 88 characters
  long, while the quotation contains 83 letters.

  In fact, it is possible to find where Jeremiah is mentioning Micah's
  prophecy in the LXX edition.

